description: Empanadas & More is taking crispy, flaky handheld pastries through the streets of Columbus, and with such a vast selection of delicious flavors, you’ll just have to come try them all. They’re serving up empanadas with seasoned ground beef, juicy shredded chicken, savory pulled pork, as well as a few fun ones like cheeseburger, pepperoni pizza, and so much more. You’ll also find some other tasty Puerto Rican dishes like rice with pigeon peas, and fried plantains, just to name a couple. Next time your stomach is feeling empty, come “feed your need” for Empanadas & More at this awesome trailer!
name: Empanadas & More
